      <title>COP29 协议存争议，气候合作面临危机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/contentious-cop29-deal-shows-climate-cooperation-fraying-edges-2024-11-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日上午，在巴库气候峰会闭幕会议上，当 COP29 主席穆赫塔尔·巴巴耶夫走上讲台，希望就全球气候融资达成来之不易的协议时，他带来了两篇演讲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/contentious-cop29-deal-shows-climate-cooperation-fraying-edges-2024-11-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 05:08:13 GMT</pubDate>
