    <item>
      <title>面对 COP29 气候信息混杂，企业寻求细节</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/business-seeks-details-face-mixed-cop29-climate-messages-2024-11-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果各国明年能够出台具有明确市场和投资政策的气候计划，COP29 就金融和碳市场达成的协议将为商界带来数十亿美元的资金流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/business-seeks-details-face-mixed-cop29-climate-messages-2024-11-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 05:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
